<agent>unix</agent>
<description>Report the mounted devices information on the target machine at scan time using the following commands.
/bin/df -h /bin/lsblk /bin/mount -l

This plugin only reports on the tools available on the system and omits any tool that did not return information when the command was ran.</description>
